data$delivery_mode <- factor(data$delivery_mode)

data$ <- factor(data$)
data$ <- factor(data$)
data$district <- factor(data$district, levels = c("","","","","","",
                                                  "", "","","","","",
                                                  "","","",""))
data$shop_type <- factor(data$shop_type, levels = c("","","","","",""))

n <- nrow(data)
model <- lm(log_recent_order_num~log_average_cost+delivery_mode
            +log_float_delivery_fee+log_float_minimum_order_amount
            +order_lead_time+district+++manjian_discount
           +other_activities+new_user+open_time
           +open08+open12+open18+open23+shop_type
           +is_new+is_premium,data=data)
lm.bic <- step(model, direction = "both", k = log(n), trace = T)

coef = lm.bic$coefficients

district_coef['district'] = c("","","","","",
                              "", "","","","","",

                            levels =c('1','0'),
                            labels = c("",""))
